      <title>莱因哈特通过入股铜金项目扩大厄瓜多尔的发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/rinehart-expands-ecuador-push-with-stake-in-copper-gold-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚女首富吉娜·莱因哈特 (Gina Rinehart) 通过入股一个极具前景的铜金项目，扩大了自己在南美洲的足迹。]]></description>
