    <item>
      <title>拜登总统称中国“仇外”，为美国实力辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-18/biden-calls-china-xenophobic-makes-case-for-us-growth-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统称中国“仇外”，同时强调了这个亚洲国家的经济困境，因为他在摇摆州宾夕法尼亚州的竞选活动中试图证明美国的经济实力。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-18/biden-calls-china-xenophobic-makes-case-for-us-growth-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:03:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登总统表示，美国钢铁公司“保证”仍为美国所有</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-18/us-steel-guaranteed-to-stay-american-owned-biden-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登誓言将继续保留美国钢铁公司的美国所有权，并呼吁对中国钢铁和铝征收更高的关税，因为他试图在 11 月大选前吸引工会工人。凯伦·利 (Karen Leigh) 接受彭博电视台报道。
 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-18/us-steel-guaranteed-to-stay-american-owned-biden-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元、韩元开始扭转跌势，亚洲股市上涨：市场收尾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周四上涨，因当局对美元走强的抵制有助于稳定货币并恢复对该地区金融市场的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 22:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔出售 2633 亿日元债券，利差收紧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/berkshire-targets-narrower-spreads-on-new-yen-bond-deal-as-boj-bets-ebb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃伦·巴菲特的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司(Berkshire Hathaway Inc.)在该公司自2019年首次发行日元债券以来最大的日元债券交易中定价了2,633亿日元（合17.1亿美元）债券，这引发了人们对这可能会增加日本股票持有量的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/berkshire-targets-narrower-spreads-on-new-yen-bond-deal-as-boj-bets-ebb</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦会见日本、韩国同行以加强经济联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-japan-south-korea-triad-extends-to-finance-in-yellen-sitdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦在首次三边金融会议后发表的联合声明中注意到日本和韩国同行对汇率大幅下跌的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-japan-south-korea-triad-extends-to-finance-in-yellen-sitdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:54:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国和新西兰同意恢复直航航班</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/thailand-new-zealand-to-resume-direct-flights-elevate-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国和新西兰同意在疫情导致空中交通中断后恢复直航，两国领导人誓言在未来二十年将双边贸易额增加两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/thailand-new-zealand-to-resume-direct-flights-elevate-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:20:34 GMT</pubDate>
